"I-Google Fit ingalandela ngokuzenzakalela umsebenzi, njengokuhamba noma ukugijima, ukusebenzisa ifoni yakho noma ukuxhuma amadivayisi agqokekayo.

I-akhawunti ayivumelekile, sicela ukhethe enye i-akhawunti.
Ayikwazi ukusungula ukuxhumeka okuthembekile kuseva. Sicela uhlole izilungiselelo zakho zenethiwekhi noma ungene ngemvume emuva kwesikhathi.

Ulwazi lomsebenzi lufaka izinhlobo zomsebenzi (ukugijima, ukuhamba ngezinyawo, ukuhamba ngebhayisikili njll), izinyathelo, amakhalori, nedatha ye-accelerometer. Izinzwa zomzimba zinikeza ukufinyelela kudatha efana nesilinganiso senhliziyo, ubude, nesisindo. I-Google Fit izokwazi ukufinyelela kumsebenzi nedatha yenzwa yomzimba egcinwe yizinhlelo zokusebenza ezixhumeke ku-Google Fit. Ungasusa lolu lwazi lomsebenzi noma kunini Kuzilungiselelo ze-Google Fit.
Umsebenzi nolwazi lenzwa yomzimba lungaphathwa ku-Google Fit futhi luzofinyeleleka kuzinhlelo zokusebenza ezinemvume yakho.

I-Google Fit ingasebenzisa ulwazi lwendawo yakho ukuze kulondolozwe imizila yemisebenzi yakho kuphinde kubalwe ulwazi olufana nesivinini sakho nebanga. Ungavala indawo ye-Fit ngokucacisiwe uphinde ubuke noma ususe amaseshini omsebenzi wakho kuzilungiselelo ze-Fit.

"Umlando wendawo ukusiza ukuthi uthole ulwazi olubalulekile - isibonelo, ukuqagela kokuhamba okuzenzakalelayo, imiphumela yosesho ethuthukisiwe, nezikhangiso ezibalulekile ngaphakathi nangaphandle kwe-Google - ngokudala imephu eyimfihlo yalapho uya khona namadivayisi akho angene ngemvume.
